<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger.SeverityFilter" Title="SeverityFilter enumeration" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger">ILogger</PageRef> ->
    SeverityFilter
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>SeverityFilter</TypeRef> enumeration defines bit-mask filters used by <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager">LogManager</PageRef> and log targets to decide which severities should be included.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      The values ending in <TypeRef>OrHigher</TypeRef> include all severities at that priority or above it. For example, <TypeRef>WarningOrHigher</TypeRef> includes Critical, Error, and Warning messages. Exact severity values such as <TypeRef>Warning</TypeRef> include only that one severity.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Bitwise <TypeRef>operator|</TypeRef>, <TypeRef>operator|=</TypeRef>, <TypeRef>operator&amp;</TypeRef>, and <TypeRef>operator&amp;=</TypeRef> overloads are provided for combining or testing filter masks.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <EnumMemberList>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="None">
        Specifies that no severity should pass the filter.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="CriticalOrHigher">
        Includes only critical messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="ErrorOrHigher">
        Includes critical and error messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="WarningOrHigher">
        Includes critical, error, and warning messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="InfoOrHigher">
        Includes critical, error, warning, and informational messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="DebugOrHigher">
        Includes critical, error, warning, informational, and debug messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="TraceOrHigher">
        Includes every defined severity value.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Critical">
        Includes only critical messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Error">
        Includes only error messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Warning">
        Includes only warning messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Info">
        Includes only informational messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Debug">
        Includes only debug messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Trace">
        Includes only trace messages.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="All">
        Includes all severities represented by the filter mask.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
    </EnumMemberList>
  </Section>
